  <entry>
    <title>从零搭建 Hexo 博客并部署到 GitHub Pages</title>
    <link href="/2026/05/15/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <url>/2026/05/15/%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="环境准备"><a href="#环境准备" class="headerlink" title="环境准备"></a>环境准备</h2><ul><li>Node.js（v18+）</li><li>Git</li><li>GitHub 账号</li><li>一个编辑器（我用的是 Trae CN）</li></ul><h2 id="一、初始化-Hexo-博客"><a href="#一、初始化-Hexo-博客" class="headerlink" title="一、初始化 Hexo 博客"></a>一、初始化 Hexo 博客</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 安装 Hexo CLI</span><br>npm install -g hexo-cli<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 初始化博客目录</span><br>hexo init my-blog<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> my-blog<br>npm install<br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 本地预览</span><br>hexo server<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 访问 http://localhost:4000</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="二、配置博客信息"><a href="#二、配置博客信息" class="headerlink" title="二、配置博客信息"></a>二、配置博客信息</h2><p>编辑 <code>_config.yml</code>：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">title:</span> <span class="hljs-string">你的博客名称</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;副标题&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">description:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;博客描述&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">author:</span> <span class="hljs-string">你的名字</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">language:</span> <span class="hljs-string">zh-CN</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">timezone:</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;Asia/Shanghai&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-attr">url:</span> <span class="hljs-string">https://你的用户名.github.io</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="三、安装主题"><a href="#三、安装主题" class="headerlink" title="三、安装主题"></a>三、安装主题</h2><p>推荐 Fluid 主题，通过 npm 安装：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">npm install --save hexo-theme-fluid<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后修改 <code>_config.yml</code>：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">theme:</span> <span class="hljs-string">fluid</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复制主题默认配置到项目根目录以便自定义：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> node_modules/hexo-theme-fluid/_config.yml _config.fluid.yml<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编辑 <code>_config.fluid.yml</code> 可修改首页副标题、导航栏等。</p><h2 id="四、配置-Git-和-SSH"><a href="#四、配置-Git-和-SSH" class="headerlink" title="四、配置 Git 和 SSH"></a>四、配置 Git 和 SSH</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 配置 Git 用户信息</span><br>git config --global user.name <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的GitHub用户名&quot;</span><br>git config --global user.email <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 生成 SSH 密钥</span><br>ssh-keygen -t ed25519 -C <span class="hljs-string">&quot;你的邮箱&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 查看公钥，复制到 GitHub Settings → SSH and GPG keys</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">cat</span> ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="五、创建-GitHub-仓库"><a href="#五、创建-GitHub-仓库" class="headerlink" title="五、创建 GitHub 仓库"></a>五、创建 GitHub 仓库</h2><ol><li>打开 <a href="https://github.com/new">https://github.com/new</a></li><li>仓库名必须是 <strong><code>你的用户名.github.io</code></strong></li><li>选择 Public</li><li>不要勾选任何初始化选项</li><li>点击 Create repository</li></ol><h2 id="六、部署到-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#六、部署到-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="六、部署到 GitHub Pages"></a>六、部署到 GitHub Pages</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 安装部署插件</span><br>npm install --save hexo-deployer-git<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在 <code>_config.yml</code> 末尾添加：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs yaml"><span class="hljs-attr">deploy:</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">type:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">repo:</span> <span class="hljs-string">git@github.com:你的用户名/你的用户名.github.io.git</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">branch:</span> <span class="hljs-string">main</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成并部署：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">hexo clean<br>hexo generate<br>hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="七、开启-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#七、开启-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="七、开启 GitHub Pages"></a>七、开启 GitHub Pages</h2><ol><li>打开仓库的 <strong>Settings → Pages</strong></li><li>Source 选择 <strong>Deploy from a branch</strong></li><li>Branch 选择 <strong>main</strong>，文件夹选 <strong>&#x2F; (root)</strong></li><li>点击 Save</li></ol><p>等 1~2 分钟，访问 <code>https://你的用户名.github.io</code> 即可看到博客。</p><h2 id="日常写文章流程"><a href="#日常写文章流程" class="headerlink" title="日常写文章流程"></a>日常写文章流程</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 新建文章</span><br>hexo new <span class="hljs-string">&quot;文章标题&quot;</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 在 source/_posts/ 找到 .md 文件，用编辑器写内容</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 格式要求：头部信息用 --- 包裹</span><br><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 发布</span><br>hexo clean<br>hexo generate<br>hexo deploy<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文章格式示例：</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">---<br>title: 文章标题<br>date: 2026-05-15 09:00:00<br>tags:<br><span class="hljs-bullet">  -</span> 标签1<br>categories:<br><span class="hljs-section">  - 分类1</span><br><span class="hljs-section">---</span><br><br>正文内容...<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><strong>注意：</strong> PowerShell 不支持 <code>&amp;&amp;</code> 连接命令，要用 <code>;</code> 分隔，或分行执行。</p></blockquote>]]></content>
    
    
